        public int compare(java.lang.Integer obj1,
          java.lang.Integer obj2)
        Description copied from interface: CompareObjects
        This method will return a comparison of the two objects. It should return the following values based upon comparing obj1 and obj2 (1) if obj1 < obj2 return -1 (2) if obj1 == obj2 return 0 (2) if obj1 > obj2 return 1
